statement.tex:
\\ \textbf{Right or wrong? }\text{The minimum, maximum}\\
			\text{values for }f(x) = x^2 + 2\text{ and hence }\text{the}\\
			\textbf{range}\text{ will be as follows.}

reason.tex:
\text{For }f(x) = 2-3x,\text{ we did say }x\gt 0, x\in\mathbb{R}.\\
			\text{Hence, }x = -1\text{ is not allowed. Know the}\\
			\text{function before you work with it.}
